Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.15,0:00:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.07,0:00:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.73,0:00:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.91,0:00:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.08,0:00:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you just have to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words lured men\Nto the Grand Line in pursuit of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.59,0:00:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,dreams greater than they've\Never dared to imagine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.17,0:00:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time\Nknown as the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.97,0:00:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.73,0:00:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.98,0:01:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.45,0:01:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.08,0:01:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.71,0:01:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.47,0:01:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.47,0:01:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.18,0:01:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.44,0:01:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.94,0:01:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.61,0:01:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.49,0:01:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:02:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.22,0:02:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\N"Zeff and Sanji's dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Illusory All Blue!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.14,0:02:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN] I don't care how much\Nof a bad ass he used to be;
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.77,0:02:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,now he's just a cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have to break a\Nsweat to kill this old fart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll spare him,\Nbut you have to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't make this any\Nharder, Sanji. Just leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.74,0:02:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't force me to\Nkill both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away... Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.25,0:02:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] You look even dumber\Nat gunpoint, Old Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.17,0:02:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of example\Ndo you think you're setting
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,for all the other cooks?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.14,0:02:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah! I don't need a lecture\Nfrom a brat like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:02:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you stop\Ncalling me names?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit treating me like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.10,0:03:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji wouldn't abandon\NZeff now would he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NGhin, point that gun at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.49,0:03:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, but what if you die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.66,0:03:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji, why you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL]\NSomeone's eager to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky for you, I'd be\Nmore than happy to oblige.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be my pleasure to beat\Nyou to a bloody, lifeless pulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.21,0:03:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.46,0:03:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL]\NThe absolutely natural Pearl...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL]\NSurprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.51,0:03:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you dodge that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.02,0:03:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunts]\NBecause if I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that rat over there would\Npull the trigger on Zeff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.35,0:03:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[huffs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.19,0:03:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NWhy are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave the restaurant\Npeacefully and no one gets hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.57,0:03:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.78,0:03:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This restaurant is\Nthat old man's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] I've already\Ntaken everything else
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:03:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that man holds dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NHis power...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...his dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunts]\NSo, while I'm around...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm not gonna let anything\Nelse get taken from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEARL]\NPearl... Cymbals!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.93,0:04:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARNE]\NSanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The All Blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NYeah! It's out there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll bet it's even\Nawesomer than they say it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK A]\NStop being a doofus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just a fairy tale\Nfor seafaring cooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK B]\NDon't get me wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we've all had our little\Nfantasies about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but you gotta remember\Nthat it's just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.76,0:04:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream? Well I'm\Ngonna find the All Blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,then we'll see\Nwho's dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite the quest.\NGood luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:04:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All right there little man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, do you even know what\Nkind of place the All Blue is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[SAJNI]\NYeah, I do. I'm not an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The All Blue is a place where\Nfish from all four seas live.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There're fish from\NEast Blue, the West Blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the North Blue,\Nand the South Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.90,0:05:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,To cooks who have\Ntaken to the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,it's an irresistible paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! That place\Nis a goldmine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got fish and plants\Nfrom all over the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Any chef would jump at\Nthe chance to cook there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,True. The cooks I know would\Nrisk life and limb to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.51,0:05:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK A]\NYeah! Well, if it were real.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You think a miracle sea like the\NAll Blue could actually exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it kid,\Nit's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK C] Ha, ha! I bet\Nit's probably just a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,told by some daydreaming cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK A] Okay, enough\Nwith the silly stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out there and collect\Nsome plates, Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NHmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK A]\NAw man. What a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They left behind\Nplates and plates
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:05:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,full of this delicious grub.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK C] This one's\Nbarely been touched!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty good stuff too. I\Nthought they'd love it for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK B] If you ask me,\Nthe customers these days
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,are spoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's way gross to eat\Nthe leftovers of strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You should just let me\Nthrow that stuff away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of talk proves\Nyou gotta whole lot to learn,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so listen up, shorty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you choose life on the high\Nseas, you gotta be resourceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The ocean is a strange\Nand unpredictable place,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,where wasting food\Ncould be a fatal mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why don't you\Nhave some? Heh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.52,0:06:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK II giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[PASSENGERS screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, people!\NPanicking won't help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.44,0:06:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI, COOKS]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[SAILOR B grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.44,0:06:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS whimper]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[SAILOR C]\NThat ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Red Foot Zeff\Nand the Cook Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[SAILOR B] They're back...\Nfrom the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.93,0:07:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES chuckle]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I take it you're the\Ninfamous pirate captain
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Red Foot Zeff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Steal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] Steal everything\Nthat isn't nailed down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[PASSENGERS screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NThose bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to die at the\Nhands of those animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE 2]\NWhoa, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Killer,\Nif you're not careful,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you might just put\Nsomeone's eye out with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He got me. Look, I'm bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You mongrels\Nbetter stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK A yelps]\NSanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! You'll make them mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] A bit young\Nto have a death wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's no reason\Nnot to grant it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.15,0:07:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, you jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm dying here, then I'm\Ntakin' some of you with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:07:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that was brutal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES chuckle]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NI'm not gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here... Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...so that I can\Nfind the All Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE 3]\NHe said, "the All Blue!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE 4]\NPretty ambitious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE 1]\NOh, that's a good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Captain, should we tell the\Nlittle tyke it doesn't exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[wood cracking]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI groaning]\NNo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna draw\Nmy last breath
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,until I've seen the All Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE 3]\NCaptain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I recommend we\Nwithdraw, immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.64,0:09:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This storm is way\Nbigger than expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NAll right men, playtime's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's load up the treasure\Nand get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF grumbles]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE 2]\NThe Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE 5]\NCaptain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE 3] Why'd he risk\Nhis life for one measly kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:09:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NThe brat finally wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.24,0:11:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lucky to\Nbe alive, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI groans]\NYou!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NMoving isn't a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.21,0:11:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still pretty banged up\Nfrom the beating you took.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.54,0:11:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NWhat about the ships?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NWho knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.92,0:11:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It was terrible storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Our ships were most\Nlikely destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.43,0:11:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems we're the\Nonly survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Washed ashore on\Na desolate rock,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:12:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,without so much as a\Ncoconut tree to give us food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, there are fish in the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but the rock has been curved\Nby the waves in such a manner
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that we wouldn't be\Nable to climb back up,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,if we ever went down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sad, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all your fault, Old Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] You can whine all\Nyou want, it won't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.91,0:12:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If nobody comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll just dry up and become\Ntwo more skeletons in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Skeletons?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] That bag there...\NIt's your share of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] It's some of the\Nfood that washed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.51,0:12:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Should be about five days worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not much, but it's\Nbetter than nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ration it out,\Nit'll last longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,so use your head when you eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing we're\Nboth cooks, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.06,0:12:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.23,0:12:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that bag your\Nshare of the food?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.27,0:12:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You got way more than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.94,0:12:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You fat, old pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NOf course I get more food...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a grown man, so I\Nneed more to survive
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,than a runt like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be grateful that\NI'm sharing any of it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.17,0:13:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't expect any pity\Nfrom me, you little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] Get to the other side of\Nthis rock and watch for ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me know as\Nsoon as you see one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, don't bother talkin'\Nto me or movin' from your post.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll just waste energy,\Nand we can't afford that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.78,0:13:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.24,0:13:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you, gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying anything\Nif I see a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.87,0:13:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine. I have five\Nwhole days worth of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll definitely see a ship\Nor two before I run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.08,0:13:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to be extra safe, I'll\Ndivide it up for twenty days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's more than enough\Ntime to get rescued.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:13:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess all I gotta\Ndo now is sit and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:14:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy! I'll make it\Nthrough this thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.03,0:14:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't see a ship today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.41,0:14:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all right.\NIt'll only be a few more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NI don't wanna die...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.06,0:14:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI weakly]\NThis is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One moldy piece of bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK A]\NAw man, what a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.66,0:15:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They left behind\Nplates and plates
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,full of this\Ndelicious grub.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] It's way gross to eat\Nthe leftovers of strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You should just let me\Nthrow that stuff away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.21,0:15:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why don't you\Nhave some... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NNo way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,--[sniffling]\N--[stomach growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NMy last piece of bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NI wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the geezer dead yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.34,0:16:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gasps]\NHe's alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's still got food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:16:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so much left!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.49,0:17:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to get that food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fair that he has\Nso much more than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.03,0:17:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, this is all his fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.59,0:17:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] What're you\Ndoing here, ya' brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] Are you here\Nbecause ya' saw a ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I came over here to\Nsteal your food, Old Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna kill\Nme for it, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon enough I'll starve, so\Nit makes no difference to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[huffs]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[clattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] Didn't I tell you\Nnot to come over here
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,unless you saw a ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it's... food.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NStrange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We have all this money and\Nyet, we're going to starve.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.56,0:18:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[labored breathing]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[labored breathing]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] Hey! What's\Ngoing on here, Old Man?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your food?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You had to have eaten something!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.37,0:18:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.34,0:18:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.81,0:18:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NIt was then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.11,0:19:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it wasn't a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to save me, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.54,0:19:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The food...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you give me all\Nof the food you had?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And you had to have known\Nthat without that leg,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd never be a pirate again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] You old fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make sense to\Nsacrifice so much for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.23,0:19:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NBecause...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.86,0:19:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,For my entire life I've\Nhad the same dream as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The All Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:20:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But... your men said\Nthat it doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.25,0:20:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NOf course it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.08,0:20:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time comes,\Nhead to the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where the All\NBlue is sure to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My days as a pirate are done,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.18,0:20:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but you have your\Nwhole life to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.97,0:20:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't die, now! Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Old Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.56,0:20:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NI wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.98,0:20:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How many men have lost their\Nlives cursing the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,knowing that it will\Nsoon be their grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.24,0:20:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the first time\NI've been hungry enough
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to look death in the eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and my thoughts are\Nthe same each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.29,0:20:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It is always my deepest wish
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.50,0:20:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that there be a restaurant\Nin the middle of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NA restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.55,0:20:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NYeah, I was thinking that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,if I make it out\Nof this mess alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to build a restaurant\Nas my final purpose in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:21:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! And I'll\Neven help you do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, don't die okay? Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.81,0:21:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A weak little brat like you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't be much\Ngood for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll become strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.11,0:21:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]\NSo... Don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.78,0:21:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.54,0:21:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The geezer needs help!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.18,0:21:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.81,0:21:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.39,0:21:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here! Help us!\NThis way! Please, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.73,0:21:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.23,0:21:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Help, help! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.74,0:21:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NThat old coot...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave up his leg\Nso that I could live!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.29,0:22:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.33,0:22:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way to repay the\Nold geezer for his kindness,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.25,0:22:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,unless I risk my life for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.18,0:22:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why are you\Nstanding, Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.22,0:22:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay down!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.10,0:22:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,'Fraid I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.73,0:22:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little too\Nmuch like giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.35,0:22:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.98,0:22:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! They'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.11,0:22:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.82,0:22:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.41,0:22:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! That is so very\Nrefined of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.33,0:22:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But, this restaurant\Nwill be closing soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.33,0:22:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and it'll open again\Nfor business...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.54,0:22:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...as a pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.04,0:22:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.96,0:22:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.00,0:22:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghin'll shoot the old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.63,0:22:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY, CARNE gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.80,0:22:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK D]\NWhat'd he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.55,0:23:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Gum-Gum!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.51,0:23:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Battle-Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.23,0:23:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.61,0:23:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.23,0:23:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.99,0:23:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.12,0:23:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.83,0:23:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.33,0:23:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.05,0:23:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.97,0:23:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.60,0:23:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.90,0:23:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.74,0:24:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.78,0:24:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.74,0:24:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.00,0:24:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.87,0:24:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.47,0:24:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] They call themselves\Nthe strongest in the East Blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.97,0:24:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's because they\Nhad so many pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.97,0:24:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NYou sure don't mince words.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.60,0:24:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Look, it seems like\NGhin can't defeat Sanji either.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.23,0:24:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NNot quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.94,0:24:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] What were those weapons\Nthat look like dumplings?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.57,0:24:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, he wasn't an underling?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.53,0:24:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.32,0:24:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"Coolheaded, Coldhearted Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.91,0:24:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirate Fleet Chief\NCommander, Ghin!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.16,0:24:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!

